title: Grateful Dead Live at Knickerbocker Arena on 1991-03-23
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Bertha, Walkin' Blues, Friend Of The Devil, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Loser, Cassidy, New Speedway Boogie

Set 2

Iko Iko, Saint Of Circumstance, Ship of Fools, Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> All Along The Watchtower-> Morning Dew-> One More Saturday Night, E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

reviews.review_text: Smokin' They came out hot with Jack Straw and kept going!  Dreamy drums and super space.  Absolutely one of the best Morning Dews I've heard.  Literally in tears. I was in a puddle and then One more Saturday didn't hit me right I will say.  Gorgeous encore Knockin'  man I miss y'all.  And you too.
